00:29:37,577 --> 00:29:38,589
<i>In just a few minutes</i>

517
00:29:38,625 --> 00:29:41,295
<i>we should be receiving a signal</i>
<i>from the spacecraft.</i>

518
00:29:41,795 --> 00:29:44,799
<i>It's important to know that it takes</i>
<i>- 21 minutes. for the signal</i>

519
00:29:44,835 --> 00:29:46,014
<i>from Mars to reach Earth.</i>

520
00:29:46,050 --> 00:29:48,755
<i>We have no way of communicating</i>
<i>with Capricorn One</i>

521
00:29:49,012 --> 00:29:52,140
<i>and what we will see actually</i>
