522
00:29:52,177 --> 00:29:53,718
<i>This is Capricorn Control.</i>

523
00:29:53,975 --> 00:29:55,304
We're getting something now.

524
00:29:55,936 --> 00:29:58,397
We are changing to a secondary
frequency.

525
00:29:58,433 --> 00:30:00,790
<i>Houston, this is Capricorn One.</i>

526
00:30:00,827 --> 00:30:03,147
<i>CM-LM separation was normal.</i>

527
00:30:03,402 --> 00:30:06,273
<i>I have CM visual contact</i>
<i>through port window.</i>

528
00:30:06,573 --> 00:30:09,281
<i>Delta-V burn time: 3.3 seconds.</i>

529
00:30:09,317 --> 00:30:11,989
<i>3.3 seconds. burn is correct.</i>

530
00:30:12,371 --> 00:30:15,538
<i>We should be hearing from</i>
<i>the CM... soon.</i>

531
00:30:15,666 --> 00:30:17,585
<i>- Houston, this is Capricorn CM.</i>
- Just wait.

532
00:30:17,621 --> 00:30:18,925
<i>I see the LM.</i>

533
00:30:18,961 --> 00:30:22,131
5 minutes. after the landing,
that asshole Price'll be callin'

