590
00:33:51,360 --> 00:33:54,488
<i>Because the time delay would make</i>
<i>a conversation impossible,</i>

591
00:33:54,525 --> 00:33:56,490
<i>the crew has taken a prerecorded</i>
<i>message</i>

592
00:33:56,527 --> 00:33:58,465
from the President with them.

593
00:33:58,501 --> 00:34:00,403
<i>This is Capricorn Control.</i>

594
00:34:00,662 --> 00:34:02,455
<i>Houston, we're activating</i>
the camera.

595
00:34:02,492 --> 00:34:03,237
<i>Roger, Capricorn.</i>

596
00:34:06,209 --> 00:34:08,249
<i>Houston, you should have</i>
<i>a picture now.</i>

597
00:34:08,670 --> 00:34:11,755
- We have a pretty good picture now.
