598
00:34:13,259 --> 00:34:14,967
<i>I am on the ladder.</i>

599
00:34:15,678 --> 00:34:17,470
<i>Houston, the suit is functional.</i>

600
00:34:17,680 --> 00:34:20,385
<i>The ladder is steady.</i>
<i>I am three steps from the bottom.</i>

601
00:34:22,644 --> 00:34:24,388
<i>I'm two steps from the bottom.</i>

602
00:34:28,067 --> 00:34:29,691
<i>Houston, I'm on the bottom step.</i>

603
00:34:32,071 --> 00:34:34,858
<i>Houston, I am gonna set foot</i>
<i>on the surface.</i>

604
00:34:36,701 --> 00:34:37,946
Ready slow-mo.

605
00:34:38,662 --> 00:34:40,156
<i>I take this step</i>

606
00:34:40,539 --> 00:34:42,199
<i>in the journey of peace</i>

607
00:34:42,875 --> 00:34:44,452
<i>for all mankind.</i>

608
00:34:44,918 --> 00:34:45,914
Take slow-mo!

609
00:34:51,968 --> 00:34:54,424
<i>Houston, I am on the surface.</i>

610
00:34:54,804 --> 00:34:56,678
Roger, Capricorn. We copy.

611
00:34:56,932 --> 00:34:58,723
<i>I am starting to walk now.</i>

612
00:35:00,602 --> 00:35:04,766
<i>Houston, the surface is solid.</i>
<i>Visibility is good.</i>

613
00:35:05,191 --> 00:35:06,768
<i>I'm walking toward the camera</i>
<i>now.</i>

614
00:35:09,070 --> 00:35:10,481
<i>The footing is solid.</i>

615
00:35:12,240 --> 00:35:14,197
<i>Surface seems powdery.</i>

616
00:35:14,910 --> 00:35:16,618
<i>I am picking up the camera now.</i>

617
00:35:17,663 --> 00:35:19,121
<i>I have the camera.</i>

618
00:35:20,082 --> 00:35:22,240
<i>The picture will get shaky</i>
<i>for a while.</i>

619
00:35:24,670 --> 00:35:25,999
<i>The footing is good.</i>

620
00:35:28,549 --> 00:35:31,337
<i>Houston, I am setting</i>
<i>the camera down now.</i>

621
00:35:32,721 --> 00:35:34,548
<i>The rocks seem very porous.</i>

622
00:35:36,016 --> 00:35:38,223
<i>Houston, I am outside the hatch.</i>

623
00:35:39,019 --> 00:35:40,597
<i>Houston, I am on the ladder.</i>

624
00:35:42,023 --> 00:35:43,185
Ready slow-mo.

625
00:35:43,983 --> 00:35:45,727
<i>Houston, I'm stepping</i>
onto the surface

626
00:35:46,027 --> 00:35:46,809
Take slow-mo!

627
00:35:53,785 --> 00:35:55,493
<i>Houston, I am on the surface.</i>

628
00:35:56,205 --> 00:35:58,577
<i>We are going to set the flag</i>
<i>on the surface.</i>

629
00:35:59,333 --> 00:36:02,508
<i>We do not claim this planet</i>
<i>in the name of America.</i>

630
00:36:02,545 --> 00:36:05,961
<i>We claim it in the name of all the</i>
<i>the people of the planet Earth.</i>

631
00:36:06,299 --> 00:36:09,052
<i>We hope that our visit will increase</i>
<i>the understanding</i>

632
00:36:09,089 --> 00:36:10,392
<i>of the human race.</i>

633
00:36:10,429 --> 00:36:12,353
Walker should be activating
the tape soon

634
00:36:12,389 --> 00:36:14,512
with the prerecorded message
from the President.

635
00:36:16,143 --> 00:36:17,970
<i>Houston, I am starting the tape.</i>

636
00:36:18,270 --> 00:36:20,278
<i>"To the men of Capricorn One.</i>

637
00:36:20,314 --> 00:36:23,066
<i>I bring you greetings</i>
<i>from your fellow Americans</i>

638
00:36:23,693 --> 00:36:25,982
<i>and all the citizens of the world."</i>

639
00:36:26,488 --> 00:36:28,564
<i>You are so far away.</i>

640
00:36:28,949 --> 00:36:32,069
<i>It takes light more than 20 min.</i>
<i>to reach you from here.</i>

641
00:36:32,494 --> 00:36:34,736
<i>One could say not only light,</i>

642
00:36:35,206 --> 00:36:37,245
<i>one could say time.</i>

643
00:36:37,834 --> 00:36:40,669
<i>You are in another time from us,</i>

644
00:36:41,129 --> 00:36:42,160
<i>the future.</i>

645
00:36:42,630 --> 00:36:44,374
<i>We will never be the same,</i>

646
00:36:45,008 --> 00:36:46,515
<i>for this moment</i>

647
00:36:46,551 --> 00:36:48,710
<i>more than any moment</i>
<i>in our history,</i>

648
00:36:49,096 --> 00:36:51,390
<i>has made all of the people</i>
<i>in the world realize</i>

649
00:36:51,427 --> 00:36:53,182
<i>that we are part of the planet,</i>

650
00:36:53,768 --> 00:36:55,392
<i>that is part of the system,</i>

651
00:36:56,062 --> 00:36:57,853
<i>that is part of the Universe.</i>

652
00:36:58,857 --> 00:37:01,644
<i>We are a small energetic species,</i>

653
00:37:02,402 --> 00:37:06,649
<i>capable of pettiness,</i>
<i>yet capable of brilliance.</i>

654
00:37:07,032 --> 00:37:09,570
<i>We know how bad we can be,</i>

655
00:37:10,369 --> 00:37:13,573
<i>now you, the men</i>
<i>of Capricorn One,</i>

656
00:37:14,207 --> 00:37:16,912
<i>have shown us how wonderful</i>
<i>we can be</i>

657
00:37:17,460 --> 00:37:20,580
<i>by showing us how high</i>
<i>we can reach.</i>

658
00:37:21,840 --> 00:37:24,794
<i>You have crossed</i>
<i>the last great frontier</i>

659
00:37:25,386 --> 00:37:27,462
<i>and you have shown us</i>
<i>what we are:</i>

660
00:37:27,972 --> 00:37:28,968
<i>people.</i>

661
00:37:29,390 --> 00:37:32,676
<i>Of different colors and religions</i>
<i>and ideologies,</i>

662
00:37:33,227 --> 00:37:35,849
<i>however, a single people.</i>

663
00:37:36,982 --> 00:37:39,140
<i>You are the basic truth in us.</i>

664
00:37:39,609 --> 00:37:41,353
<i>You are the reality.</i>

665
00:37:42,696 --> 00:37:45,068
<i>We will never let you down</i>

666
00:37:46,033 --> 00:37:48,655
<i>and we will always be grateful."</i>

