01:28:42,791 --> 01:28:43,989
Which one?

1318
01:28:46,879 --> 01:28:48,587
What direction was he going?

1319
01:28:51,801 --> 01:28:55,253
Brubaker is going West.
Put everybody West.

1320
01:29:06,859 --> 01:29:07,855
Caulfield.

1321
01:29:08,486 --> 01:29:09,517
Right now?

1322
01:29:09,737 --> 01:29:10,816
Okay.

