1350
01:30:18,641 --> 01:30:20,565
- and you think I won't believe you?
- My car!

1351
01:30:20,601 --> 01:30:22,113
Someone tampered
with my car!

1352
01:30:22,150 --> 01:30:23,948
The one you decided to go
swimming with?

1353
01:30:23,985 --> 01:30:26,154
They did something to it!
I couldn't stop it!

1354
01:30:26,191 --> 01:30:27,269
Can you prove that?

1355
01:30:29,491 --> 01:30:30,866
The police said...

1356
01:30:32,453 --> 01:30:36,082
- They said that nothing was wrong.
